address1: Bank of East Asia Harbour View Centre
longBusinessSummary: Shoucheng Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the management and operation of car parking assets. The company operates through Parking, and Infrastructure and Real Estate Fund Management segments. It also manages private, infrastructure, and real estate funds and investments; and provides equity investments. The company was formerly known as Shougang Concord International Enterprises Company Limited and changed its name to Shoucheng Holdings Limited in May 2020. Shoucheng Holdings Limited is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
